  <summary date="2023-03-13T19:34:12Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Apprenticeships to College Act

This bill requires the Department of Labor to enter into an interagency agreement with the Department of Education to promote and support integration and alignment of programs under the national apprenticeship system with secondary, two- and four-year postsecondary, and adult education.</summary>
